      "1\u2264Pi\u22642\u22c5N1 \\leq P_i \\leq 2 \\cdot N1\u2264Pi\u200b\u22642\u22c5N",
      "Pi\u2260PjP_i \\neq P_jPi\u200b\ue020=Pj\u200b for 1\u2264i&lt;j\u2264N1 \\leq i \\lt j \\leq N1\u2264i&lt;j\u2264N",
      "The sum of NNN over all test cases won't exceed 10610^6106."
